This paper deals with image encryption and decryption using neural networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also explores the use of deep neural networks for cryptanalysis, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with lossy compression, which could fall under information theory (cs.IT).
